    {
      "card": {
        "bgColor": "var(--gray-3)",
        "label": "Lesson 5 • Talking about company strategy",
        "descriptions": [
          {
            "description": [
              {
                "text": "Andy and Laura work for Saltonica, a maker of cell phones. Sales have been slow lately, so Andy is recommending the company adopt a new strategy."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Andy: "
            },
            {
              "text": "My team has come up with a new strategy. We can’t continue being "
            },
            {
              "markedText": "fast followers"
            },
            {
              "text": ". We need to start developing our own "
            },
            {
              "markedText": "cutting-edge"
            },
            {
              "text": " technologies."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Laura: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Why? We’ve been fast followers for the past ten years. "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"Why mess with success?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Andy: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Success? "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"Get with the program"
            },
            {
              "text":	". Our sales are way down. Our "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"cash cow"
            },
            {
              "text":	", the Model 8B, only sold 900 units last month!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Laura: "
            },
            {
              "text": "I can understand why. That phone’s a relic.* It’s been around for over three years. What about our new phones?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Andy: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Our latest model cell phone was a "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"real dog"
            },
            {
              "text":	"! It sold only 20 percent of our sales forecast."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Laura: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Any idea why? "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Andy: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Product life cycles are much shorter now than before. New technologies are developed at a much faster rate."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Laura: "
            },
            {
              "text": "So what are we supposed to do?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Andy: "
            },
            {
              "text": "We need to become much more innovative as a company. Instead of producing "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"me-too products"
            },
            {
              "text":	", we need to "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"leapfrog our competitors"
            },
            {
              "text":	"."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Laura: "
            },
            {
              "text": "How do we do that?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Andy: "
            },
            {
              "markedText": "For starters"
            },
            {
              "text":	", we need to "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"beef up"
            },
            {
              "text":	" our R&D** department. We need to develop differentiated products which we can sell "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"at a premium"
            },
            {
              "text":	"."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Laura: "
            },
            {
              "text": "As a next step, let’s "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"get buy-in"
            },
            {
              "text":	" from our marketing and sales directors."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Andy: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Right. We should get everyone "
            },
            {
              "markedText":	"on the same page"
            },
            {
              "text":	"."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
